message.body: Bahahahha! Who is he name dropping? Me? And HEY
HEY, I'm here with Megan and JT and others. JT and I are playing in the bands before and after him...he mentioned New Ulm and we made some connection points
Hilarious. He's totally a business man. My brother made some music with him back when. And also, how are you?
I'm swell. Enjoying the graduate life. Interviewing with USPIRG next weekend in Chicago. Hopin'. YOU?
What's that? Im gewd. On spring break! Missing home. Say hey to everyone btw!
US public interest research group. Consumer advocacy group. ''Deconstructing the master's house with the master's tools'' kinda work.
Oh you did not just talk about the masters house. I fucking love you
I figured that you're the only person I know who I could use that phrase with
Hahaha. I've labored over that metaphors. Papers and essays and shit over
